<section class="landing-screen">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-7 introduction">
                <h1 class="animate__animated animate__bounce">Hi, I'm Ellis</h1>
                <h4 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">A Mobile and Web Developer</h4>
                <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">I use code in solving problems while building beautiful applications to meet your needs, or to build stuffs just for fun!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <img class="developer-pic animate__animated animate__fadeInRight" src="images/display_pic.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="about-me">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center hiddenSection">
            <div class="col-md-6 testing hidden">
                <img class="about-me-pic" src="images/about_me.png">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 hidden">
                <h1>About Me</h1>
                <p>Ellis is a software developer based in Owerri, Imo State, Nigeria. He began his development journey at the age of 14, and built his first website using HTML and in-line CSS. He then went on to study for 5 years at the Federal Polytechnic Nekede, Owerri, graduating with a Higher National Diploma in Biochemistry in 2016. </p>
                <p>When Ellis is not writing codes, he loves watching movies, reading books/articles or playing video games with his friends.</p>
                <p>Ellis hopes to help you build phenomenal applications.</p>
                <p><span class="austin">Languages I speak:</span> Flutter & Dart, JavaScript
                </p>
                <p><span>Others:</span> HTML, CSS, NodeJS, ExpressJS, MongoDB, Git/GitHub, Bootstrap</p>
                <div class="social-icons">
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Ellisice" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook fa-2x"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/unknownaloy" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-github fa-2x"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ellisaloy/" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram fa-2x"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ellis-ifoegbu-3aa87717b/" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin fa-2x"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/Ellisice" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter fa-2x"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/10296000/chichebe?tab=profile" target="blank"><i class="fab fa-stack-overflow fa-2x"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="contact-me">
    <h1>Contact Me</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 reach-padding">
                <p class="reach-out"><span>Reach</span><span>Out!</span></p>
                <img src="images/telephone.svg" alt="image of a telephone" height="80" width="80" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <form method="POST" action="/compose">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="row">
                            <label class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Name:</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-10"><input class="form-control" type="text" name="name"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row"> <label class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Heading:</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-10"><input class="form-control" type="text" name="heading"></div>
                        </div>
                        <label>Message:</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" name="postContent" cols="20" rows="5" style="resize: none"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn" type="submit">SEND</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
